{
  "name": "🔄 [2] Automação Diários - RETRY (a cada 30min)",
  "description": "Workflow 2: Executa a cada 30min entre 8:30 e 12:00. Tenta encontrar novos diários se Workflow 1 não encontrou.",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [{"minutes": 30}]
        }
      },
      "name": "⏱️ Cron - A Cada 30min",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.cron",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Verificar se está no horário (8:30 até 12:00)\nconst agora = new Date();\nconst horaAtual = agora.getHours();\nconst minutoAtual = agora.getMinutes();\n\n// Parar se passou das 12h\nif (horaAtual >= 12) {\n  return {\n    tempoValido: false,\n    motivo: 'Passou das 12h - parando',\n    horaAtual: `${horaAtual}:${minutoAtual < 10 ? '0' : ''}${minutoAtual}`\n  };\n}\n\n// Parar se for antes das 8:30 (ex: execução noturna)\nif (horaAtual < 8 || (horaAtual === 8 && minutoAtual < 30)) {\n  return {\n    tempoValido: false,\n    motivo: 'Antes das 8:30 - não executa',\n    horaAtual: `${horaAtual}:${minutoAtual < 10 ? '0' : ''}${minutoAtual}`\n  };\n}\n\nreturn {\n  tempoValido: true,\n  horaAtual: `${horaAtual}:${minutoAtual < 10 ? '0' : ''}${minutoAtual}`,\n  tentativa: 'Workflow 2'\n};"
      },
      "name": "🕐 Checar Hora (8:30-12:00)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": [
            {"condition": "custom expression", "value": "={{ $node['Checar Hora (8:30-12:00)'].json.tempoValido }}"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "❓ Está no Horário?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [650, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://tcm.ioepa.com.br/busca/",
        "options": {
          "headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36"}
        }
      },
      "name": "🌐 Scrape TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [850, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://www.tcepa.tc.br/diario-oficial",
        "options": {
          "headers": {"User-Agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36"}
        }
      },
      "name": "🌐 Scrape TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [850, 450]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "claude-opus-4-6",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "Analise este HTML da página de busca do TCM/Pará e extraia:\n1. **data**: Data do diário mais recente em formato YYYY-MM-DD\n2. **url_pdf**: URL completa para download do PDF\n3. **titulo**: Título ou número do diário\n4. **descricao**: Breve descrição\n\nSe não encontrar, retorne data como null.\n\nRESPONDA APENAS EM JSON:\n{\"data\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"url_pdf\": \"https://...\", \"titulo\": \"...\", \"descricao\": \"...\"}\n\nHTML:\n{{ $node[\"Scrape TCM\"].json.body.substring(0, 5000) }}",
              "role": "user"
            }
          ]
        },
        "maxTokens": 600
      },
      "name": "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1050, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "model": "claude-opus-4-6",
        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "Analise este HTML da página de diários do TCE/Pará e extraia:\n1. **data**: Data do diário mais recente em formato YYYY-MM-DD\n2. **url_pdf**: URL completa para download do PDF\n3. **titulo**: Título ou número do diário\n4. **descricao**: Breve descrição\n\nSe não encontrar, retorne data como null.\n\nRESPONDA APENAS EM JSON:\n{\"data\": \"YYYY-MM-DD\", \"url_pdf\": \"https://...\", \"titulo\": \"...\", \"descricao\": \"...\"}\n\nHTML:\n{{ $node[\"Scrape TCE\"].json.body.substring(0, 5000) }}",
              "role": "user"
            }
          ]
        },
        "maxTokens": 600
      },
      "name": "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1050, 450]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "let tcmData = { orgao: 'TCM', data: null, url_pdf: null, titulo: null };\nlet tceData = { orgao: 'TCE', data: null, url_pdf: null, titulo: null };\n\ntry {\n  const tcmMsg = $node['Claude - Analisar TCM'].json.message.content;\n  tcmData = { ...tcmData, ...JSON.parse(tcmMsg) };\n} catch(e) { console.log('TCM parse error'); }\n\ntry {\n  const tceMsg = $node['Claude - Analisar TCE'].json.message.content;\n  tceData = { ...tceData, ...JSON.parse(tceMsg) };\n} catch(e) { console.log('TCE parse error'); }\n\nreturn [tcmData, tceData];"
      },
      "name": "📝 Parse Respostas",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1250, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "search",
        "table": "diarios",
        "filterBy": {
          "fields": [{"name": "orgao", "operator": "is", "value": "TCM"}]
        },
        "options": {"limit": 1, "sort": {"field": "data", "direction": "descending"}}
      },
      "name": "📊 Get Última Data TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1450, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "search",
        "table": "diarios",
        "filterBy": {
          "fields": [{"name": "orgao", "operator": "is", "value": "TCE"}]
        },
        "options": {"limit": 1, "sort": {"field": "data", "direction": "descending"}}
      },
      "name": "📊 Get Última Data TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1450, 300]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const tcmNovo = $input.all()[0].json;\nconst tceNovo = $input.all()[1].json;\nconst ultimaTcm = $node['Get Última Data TCM'].json?.records?.[0]?.data;\nconst ultimaTce = $node['Get Última Data TCE'].json?.records?.[0]?.data;\n\nconst tcmTemNovo = tcmNovo[0].data && (!ultimaTcm || tcmNovo[0].data > ultimaTcm);\nconst tceTemNovo = tceNovo[1].data && (!ultimaTce || tceNovo[1].data > ultimaTce);\n\nreturn {\n  tcm: { ...tcmNovo[0], novo: tcmTemNovo },\n  tce: { ...tceNovo[1], novo: tceTemNovo },\n  temNovo: tcmTemNovo || tceTemNovo,\n  timestamp: new Date().toISOString()\n};"
      },
      "name": "🔍 Comparar Datas",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1650, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": [
            {"condition": "custom expression", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.temNovo }}"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "✅ Encontrou Novo?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [1850, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.url_pdf }}",
        "options": {"response": {"response": {"type": "arraybuffer"}}}
      },
      "name": "⬇️ Download PDF TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [2050, 50]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.url_pdf }}",
        "options": {"response": {"response": {"type": "arraybuffer"}}}
      },
      "name": "⬇️ Download PDF TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.1,
      "position": [2050, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "file",
        "method": "upload",
        "bucket": "diarios",
        "fileName": "tcm_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.data }}.pdf",
        "fileContent": "={{ $node['Download PDF TCM'].json.body }}"
      },
      "name": "☁️ Upload TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2250, 50]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "file",
        "method": "upload",
        "bucket": "diarios",
        "fileName": "tce_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.data }}.pdf",
        "fileContent": "={{ $node['Download PDF TCE'].json.body }}"
      },
      "name": "☁️ Upload TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2250, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            {"key": "orgao", "value": "TCM"},
            {"key": "data", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.data }}"},
            {"key": "titulo", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.titulo }}"},
            {"key": "arquivo", "value": "tcm_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.data }}.pdf"},
            {"key": "url_original", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.url_pdf }}"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "💾 Inserir TCM",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2450, 50]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            {"key": "orgao", "value": "TCE"},
            {"key": "data", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.data }}"},
            {"key": "titulo", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.titulo }}"},
            {"key": "arquivo", "value": "tce_{{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.data }}.pdf"},
            {"key": "url_original", "value": "={{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tce.url_pdf }}"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "💾 Inserir TCE",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2450, 200]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "notifications",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            {"key": "msg", "value": "✅ Diário {{ $node['Comparar Datas'].json.tcm.novo ? 'TCM' : 'TCE' }} ENCONTRADO! - {{ $now.format('DD/MM/YYYY HH:mm') }}"},
            {"key": "read", "value": false},
            {"key": "tipo_notificacao", "value": "diario"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "🔔 Notificar Sucesso",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2650, 100]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios_log",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            {"key": "orgao", "value": "AMBOS"},
            {"key": "status", "value": "sucesso"},
            {"key": "data_verificada", "value": "={{ $now.format('YYYY-MM-DD') }}"},
            {"key": "mensagem", "value": "✅ SUCESSO! Diários encontrados pelo Workflow 2 às {{ $now.format('HH:mm') }}"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "📝 Log Sucesso",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [2650, 250]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "recordApi",
        "method": "insert",
        "table": "diarios_log",
        "rows": {
          "values": [
            {"key": "orgao", "value": "AMBOS"},
            {"key": "status", "value": "sem_atualizacao"},
            {"key": "data_verificada", "value": "={{ $now.format('YYYY-MM-DD') }}"},
            {"key": "mensagem", "value": "🔄 Sem novo encontrado - Tentativa às {{ $now.format('HH:mm') }} - Próxima: 30min"}
          ]
        }
      },
      "name": "📝 Log Retry",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.supabase",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1850, 450]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "⏱️ Cron - A Cada 30min": {
      "main": [[{"node": "🕐 Checar Hora (8:30-12:00)", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "🕐 Checar Hora (8:30-12:00)": {
      "main": [[{"node": "❓ Está no Horário?", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "❓ Está no Horário?": {
      "main": [
        [{"node": "🌐 Scrape TCM", "type": "main", "index": 0}, {"node": "🌐 Scrape TCE", "type": "main", "index": 0}],
        []
      ]
    },
    "🌐 Scrape TCM": {"main": [[{"node": "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCM", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "🌐 Scrape TCE": {"main": [[{"node": "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCE", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCM": {"main": [[{"node": "📝 Parse Respostas", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "🤖 Claude - Analisar TCE": {"main": [[{"node": "📝 Parse Respostas", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "📝 Parse Respostas": {"main": [[{"node": "📊 Get Última Data TCM", "type": "main", "index": 0}, {"node": "📊 Get Última Data TCE", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "📊 Get Última Data TCM": {"main": [[{"node": "🔍 Comparar Datas", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "📊 Get Última Data TCE": {"main": [[{"node": "🔍 Comparar Datas", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "🔍 Comparar Datas": {"main": [[{"node": "✅ Encontrou Novo?", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "✅ Encontrou Novo?": {
      "main": [
        [{"node": "⬇️ Download PDF TCM", "type": "main", "index": 0}, {"node": "⬇️ Download PDF TCE", "type": "main", "index": 0}],
        [{"node": "📝 Log Retry", "type": "main", "index": 0}]
      ]
    },
    "⬇️ Download PDF TCM": {"main": [[{"node": "☁️ Upload TCM", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "⬇️ Download PDF TCE": {"main": [[{"node": "☁️ Upload TCE", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "☁️ Upload TCM": {"main": [[{"node": "💾 Inserir TCM", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "☁️ Upload TCE": {"main": [[{"node": "💾 Inserir TCE", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "💾 Inserir TCM": {"main": [[{"node": "🔔 Notificar Sucesso", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "💾 Inserir TCE": {"main": [[{"node": "🔔 Notificar Sucesso", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]},
    "🔔 Notificar Sucesso": {"main": [[{"node": "📝 Log Sucesso", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]}
  }
}
